# Registra um novo usuário no sistema
POST https://clone-tabnews-ibstq1hzy-jglucianos-projects.vercel.app/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

###

